Height><Bytes>18577</Bytes><Caption /><ThumbnailUrl>/RXLImages/1013/hotel11117-Certosa-Meeting-2.thumb.jpg</ThumbnailUrl><ThumbnailWidth>70</ThumbnailWidth><ThumbnailHeight>70</ThumbnailHeight><ThumbnailBytes>2106</ThumbnailBytes><PhotoType>HotelAmenities</PhotoType></Photo><Description><Language>en</Language><Type>General</Type><Text>This traditional 4-star hotel is situated in the southwestern suburbs of Florencem surrounded by 15 acres of parkland, a few steps from the Certosa Monastery and about 6km from the historical centre. The hotel is also located 500m from the Firenze-Certosa exit off highway A1 on Via Chiantigiana; perfect location for those travelling by car and wishing to explore the surrounding Chianti region. Originally created as a guest quarters in 1400, it was enlarged in the 19th century and in 1975 it became part of the Bettoja Hotels Group. Rooms are quite spacious and are decorated in rustic Tuscan style with dark wood furniture and wood-beam ceilings. They overlook the magnificent park setting surrounding them, and have a view of the Tuscan hills and the Certosa. Single rooms are simply and tastefully furnished. Carpets and window treatments have been matched to give each room its own special feel. Double and triple rooms offer a small terrace overlooking the garden where you can relax with the morning newspaper and coffee while surrounded by nature. All bathrooms are private and include shower and tub, hairdryer, and personal accessories. The hotel offers modern meeting and banquet facilities, tennis courts, outdoor swimming pool, bar, and a charming restaurant where typical delicious Tuscan dishes are prepared and served; Lunch and dinner can also be served in the garden or by the poolside. Continental breakfast buffet is included and is served from 07:00 - 10:30am.</Text></Description><Amenity><Code>Safe</Code><Text>Safe</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>MiniBarInRoom</Code><Text>Mini-bar</Text></Amenity><Amenity><Code>HairDryer</Code><Text>Ha